{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b0fa1f92aa","title":"锡金是东北师大右派主帅","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f1fa0361b5","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":1,"articleId":"b0fa1f92aa"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"60c7e442a5","name":"文汇报"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a737139d53","type":"title","text":"锡金是东北师大右派主帅","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b0fa1f92aa"},{"id":"14e0cff8c0","type":"authors","text":"文汇报","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b0fa1f92aa"},{"id":"4100249666","type":"appellation","text":"吉林省文艺界在对右派分子王肯的批判中，揭发出一个反党集团，这个反党集团的主帅乃是一向以老作家、老诗人、老“左”派自居的东北师大教授蒋锡金。蒋锡金、王肯和李景隆结伙向党进攻。5月初蒋锡金带头在省委召集的文艺座谈会上，向党放了恶毒的第一炮，以后由王肯写了向党全面进攻的文章——“师大宗派主义发展简史”，6月初人民日报社论发表后，蒋锡金又为王肯掩护退却，指示王肯批判葛佩琦，以作烟幕，李景隆也出了许多主意充当“军师”。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b0fa1f92aa"},{"id":"813b1c5b0d","type":"paragraph","text":" ——原载《文汇报》1957年9月1日。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b0fa1f92aa"}],"page":{"id":"79397c4ca2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b0fa1f92aa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}